    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>【关于游戏】</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Chickeat Catch》是一款捕获潜行动作游戏，玩家通过捕捉作为食用鸡而闻名的Chickeat进行出售，以偿还债务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角Niwa因为家族的养鸡场经营失败而背负了债务。请帮助Niwa捕捉Chickeat，协助他偿还债务吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/b9f8a7c113c539e3e2dc2070c5af93e0.poster.avif?t=1768408261\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/b9f8a7c113c539e3e2dc2070c5af93e0.webm?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/b9f8a7c113c539e3e2dc2070c5af93e0.mp4?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>【捕获】</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chickeat是一种胆小的鸟类，一旦发现玩家便会立刻逃跑。悄悄从后面接近并将它捕获吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于那些跑得慢的Chickeat，不需要手下留情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/900c10c3cfc4c8ce292591c3c5bfa82e.poster.avif?t=1768408261\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/900c10c3cfc4c8ce292591c3c5bfa82e.webm?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/900c10c3cfc4c8ce292591c3c5bfa82e.mp4?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>【出货】</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕获的Chickeat可以从农场出货。通过出货赚取的钱来偿还债务吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使它们露出悲伤的表情，也无需怜悯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/4d96a15a697cc15700414ecfaaf6d172.poster.avif?t=1768408261\" width=640 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/4d96a15a697cc15700414ecfaaf6d172.webm?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/4d96a15a697cc15700414ecfaaf6d172.mp4?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>【农场】</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦你抓住了一只Chickeat，它就会被送到你的农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在农场里的Chickeat即使看到你也不会逃跑，所以你可以近距离观察它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以随意捕捉，想抓1000只Chickeat送到农场也没问题——<br>只要你的电脑不会崩溃就行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/5ae6e5e1578f8096be82d4f28451fb9e.poster.avif?t=1768408261\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/5ae6e5e1578f8096be82d4f28451fb9e.webm?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/5ae6e5e1578f8096be82d4f28451fb9e.mp4?t=1768408261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>【多种类的Chickeat】</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前共有25种不同的Chickeat。根据种类的不同，它们的警觉性、逃跑速度和出售价格也有所差异。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中还存在一些稀有的Chickeat，快去找找看吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/3a5a6dd8be224110a7f0e0d9f6afba29.avif?t=1768408261\" width=640 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>【5种地图】</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着故事的发展，玩家可以进入各种地图。Chickeat生活在世界各地，根据地区的不同，种类也有所不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各个地图中寻找各种各样的Chickeat吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216300/extras/9577df93ff93d5360129bfbb0acb0943.avif?t=1768408261\" width=640 height=300 /></span></p>",
